- Dell EMC Networking S4112F-ON, S4112T-ON, S4128F-ON, S4128T-ON, S4148F-ON, and S4148T-ON switches running OS10 Enterprise Edition, release 10.4.1.3 or later

IF THE VMWARE APPROVAL CONFIRMATION PDF IS NOT ATTACHED, THE QUOTE WILL BE REJECTED.
